title: ESET NOD32 Antivirus & Smart Security 9.0.386 (x86/x64)
description:
About this release
Release date: 17/07/2016
OS: Windows 10, 8.1, 8, 7, Vista, XP (Service pack 3) / Windows Home Server 2003, 2011

ESET Smart Security offers advanced detection technologies and multi-layered security features.

Designed for a low footprint, fast scanning, it packs security features and customization options for consistent and personalized security on- or offline. ESET Smart Security is built on ESET's unique heuristic technology that identifies viruses that have never been seen before.

This enables them to protect your computer proactively, in real-time, against new viruses and cyber threats that conventional signature-based antivirus products don't catch.

ESET Smart Security has all the same features as ESET NOD32 Antivirus with the addition of parental controls, antispam module, and an intelligent firewall.

ESET NOD32 Antivirus offers advanced detection technologies and multi-layered security features.

Designed for a low footprint, fast scanning, it packs security features and customization options for consistent and personalized security on- or offline. ESET NOD32 Antivirus is built on ESET's unique heuristic technology that identifies viruses that have never been seen before.

This enables them to protect your computer proactively, in real-time, against new viruses and cyber threats that conventional signature-based antivirus products don't catch.

ESET NOD32 Antivirus includes antivirus, antispyware, antirootkit and HIPS protection, removable media control, cloud-enhanced whitelisting and gamer mode.

Included
Trial Reset: box, mara-fix 1.8
License finders: MiNodLogin 4.0.2.66 + TNod 1.6.0

Note:
- Trial Reset + License finders were put within an ISO file in order to avoid possible deletion by AV software during download (mount the ISO and disable your AV before running any of these tools
